{"tid":314175,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"實習生遭工業用氣槍射肛　直腸破裂","createTime":"2017-07-09T03:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T12:42:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb26f70e01df14f35839304cd4918892862c2ef","tid":314175,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083629&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083629%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&d=9K4m331hoOOF5Vr9VFkABZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=00ae1800\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20083629%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170709&h=58cd09a6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20083629&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170709</a><br />\n<br />\n實習生遭工業用氣槍射肛　直腸破裂<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n山東青州一間學校附屬實習工廠上月25日發生一宗意外，姓劉男職員出於惡作劇心態，用吹塵槍對準男實習生肛門噴氣，強大氣流瞬間令學生的直腸破裂，職員事後被刑事拘留。<br />\n閉路電視拍下事發過程，當時姓商實習生站在機器旁，職員拿吹塵槍在身後，趁他與人聊天不注意時出手，把吹塵槍朝對方臀部噴氣。實習生即時痛苦抽搐，捂着屁股跪在地上，職員仍不以為意，為成功得手而哈哈大笑。實習生隨即被送院急救，醫生確認他直腸破裂，法醫鑑定為「重傷二級」，內地評級傷勢最嚴重為「重傷一級」。肇事職員事後被警方逮捕，他後悔自己令實習生受傷，「就是因為手不老實，沒有管住自己的手」，並承諾以後謹言慎行，「手不能再犯賤了！」<br />\n梨視頻<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n職員貪玩用吹塵槍（左圖）攻擊實習生（上圖中）。互聯網"},{"pid":"e36ce96b94389c3a9d76cc2d218b0385a2192042","tid":314175,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T03:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170709/large/a0904a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170709%2Flarge%2Fa0904a.gif&h=7cd8bb44&s={SIZE}\" /><br 